## Deploy ingress controller 

Find the ingress-nginx controller helm chart. In the k8s repo 
There are commands to install 
It will add to your repos and then run an update 

Helm install ingress-nginx ingress ingress-nginx/ingress-nginx
helm ls - will list out helm deploy and all info

kubectl get pod 
    verify nginx-controller ingress was deployed 
kubectl get service 
    ingress services should now be installed 

Create loadbalancer on AWS

Configure loadbalancer in AWS 
    create https traffic 
    ingress-nginx-controller-lb